{"tid":442320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以勒基金另類禱文：中國成為主所喜悅的模範國，成功乃上帝揀選","createTime":"2017-10-20T13:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T14:12:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"447144c73e24a36d0f7b1d9ea934326df737eaab","tid":442320,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/god-12_DhKhs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fgod-12_DhKhs_1200x0.png&h=ada026bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個無神論的政權，原來在一些香港基督教組織中已成為主所喜悅的模範國家，其成功是上帝的旨意。香港基督教組織「以勒基金」今日 (20日) 在報紙登廣告，指中國的成功是因為被上帝揀選，並「求主繼續賜福中國」。<br />\n<br />\n該基督教組織的禱文稱，「求主繼續賜褔中國，賜能加力予每位領導人，揀選中國成為一個主所喜悅的模範國家；列國雖爭相了解中國經濟成長的奧秘，但其成功的秘訣，卻是上帝的揀選」；又指「我們的國家就在禱告中和平崛起，這真是一項充滿恩典的神蹟」。<br />\n<br />\n文中又提到香港和中國的關係，「為香港與中國的緊密連結，求主使用香港人成為主的皿器」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民讀畢禱文後，「大為讚賞」這間教會發明了一個有趣的邏輯問題 &mdash; 一班基督徒祈禱叫上帝振興一個消滅基督教的國家，那麼上帝應如何是好？<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民回應該Facebook：「你私禱怎祈都OK，但以勒基金有這樣的資源去每天做影響，就必須發出有意義的影響，而不是和諧一番就算。對不起，講唔到阿門。」<br />\n<br />\n以勒基金每日均在報紙及收費電視登廣告，過往亦曾因「求神掌管全球貨幣政策」、「求主幫助正陷於打機上癮的人士」等禱文引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/society/又係以勒基金-另類禱文-中國成為主所喜悅的模範國-成功乃上帝揀選/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%8F%88%E4%BF%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%8B%92%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E5%8F%A6%E9%A1%9E%E7%A6%B1%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E6%89%80%E5%96%9C%E6%82%85%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8B-%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E4%B9%83%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%9D%E6%8F%80%E9%81%B8%2F&d=BgrpL%2Be3K6%2FJQ%2BMEeLoYgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0ad98aa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%8F%88%E4%BF%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%8B%92%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E5%8F%A6%E9%A1%9E%E7%A6%B1%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E6%89%80%E5%96%9C%E6%82%85%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8B-%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E4%B9%83%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%9D%E6%8F%80%E9%81%B8%2F&h=924ad85e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.thestandnews.com/society/又係以勒基金-另類禱文-中國成為主所喜悅的模範國-成功乃上帝揀選/</a>"},{"pid":"9ca20b160a0585ad0a0ada8bba29e20cb37b6aeb","tid":442320,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/22519584_10155126167308036_1422143799023532579_n_cC7qM_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F22519584_10155126167308036_1422143799023532579_n_cC7qM_1200x0.jpg&h=a39c4e86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4b364e0b46add2dc1acd70da2ef8389deefe7fe","tid":442320,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"刷撚錯鞋啦<br />\n無神論嚟架"},{"pid":"9c4afdb5d301675084bf53ddde4c7ffff055f3a0","tid":442320,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"5d7ae2258bfa3735bdb7995ec63a27251b0b3dfc","tid":442320,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾，不可直呼上帝名字呀，第一句就開全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f0e4a39e4d99662f56d1905d6eb8f7e92357be","tid":442320,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"大愛既表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05257231aa4a11df875bbbc810af8d739a7d42ea","tid":442320,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"而家香港真係教會多過馬會<br />\n我都諗緊 不如去讀番個神學碩士<br />\n 開返檔教會 真係財源滾滾來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}